1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
UsefulDesk — a WhatsApp-first CRM for gym businesses.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
I'm on the Settings page. I'll connect a WhatsApp Business Account.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
I click "Connect WhatsApp" to start Embedded Signup.

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,000
[public_profile] Facebook Login for Business opens.

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
I select my business portfolio.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:25,000
[business_management] The app reads the business assets I share.

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:31,000
I create a new WhatsApp Business Account.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Using WhatsApp display only, so it provisions a test phone number.

9
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:45,000
[whatsapp_business_management] The app registers the number and subscribes the WABA for webhooks.

10
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:50,000
I complete the steps and the popup closes.

11
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Back on the CRM: "Meta connected" — WhatsApp API successfully connected.

12
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
I verify with the built-in test API button. It returns success.

13
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:05,000
The credentials and phone number are live.

14
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:12,000
[whatsapp_business_messaging] I open WhatsApp on a real phone and send a message.

15
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:18,000
The message appears in my CRM's shared inbox.

16
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:24,000
I reply directly from the CRM inbox.

17
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:30,000
The reply is delivered and shows in the WhatsApp conversation on the phone.

18
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:36,000
A business connects its WhatsApp account via Embedded Signup.

19
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Our platform then sends and receives messages on their behalf.

20
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:48,000
In production, gym owners connect their number to send renewal reminders and payment follow-ups.
